  <title>lcCorrectResponse2</title>
  <shortdesc>The &lt;<keyword>lcCorrectResponse2</keyword>&gt; element in an assessment interaction
    indicates a correct response. This element replaces the
    &lt;<keyword>lcCorrectResponse</keyword>&gt; element in DITA 1.2.</shortdesc>
