      <p>In a &lt;<keyword>lcHotspot</keyword>> interaction, indicate the correct hotspot by setting
        the value attribute of &lt;<keyword>lcCorrectResponse2</keyword>> to the id of the "correct"
        area in the imagemap.</p>
